description: This Traditional Passive Antenna Offers The Finest Quality Dual Purpose Designs For Vhf & Uhf Reception; Fully Extended 39" Dipoles To Help Capture & Hold Vhf Broadcast Signals (Channels 2 Through 13) Better Than Shorter Varieties; The Flexible Uhf Loop (Channels 14 Through 69) Provides Access To The Newest Additional Channels Provided By The Digital Initiative; Will Provide 1080I & 720P Hdtv Performance When It Is Available; Heavy, Weighted Base With Attached 5 Ft Coaxial Cable & Protective Bottom
title: Zenith VN1ANTP1 Indoor Passive VHF/UHF Antenna
